        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/maani-al-akhbar:95:1",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/28/1/95/1",
        "text": [
          ": يا حسين أكرم النعمة  . قلت: جعلت فداك، وأي شئ كرامتها؟ قال: اصطناع المعروف فيما يبقى عليك."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.basel-kadem": [
            "1.\tWe were told by Muhammed bin Ali Majilawayh, may Allah be pleased with him, from his paternal uncle, Muhammed bin Abi’l-Qasim, from Muhammed bin Ali al-Sayrafi, from Sa’dan bin Muslim, from Hussain bin Na’eem, from Abu Abdillah, peace be upon him, that he said: O Hussain, be generous with the grace. I said: May I be sacrificed for you, and what thing is generosity with it? He said: To attempt doing good with what remains to you."
          ]
        }
      }
